      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[AZURE.NOTE]</ph> If you wish to learn more about the new .NET server SDK and how to add/remove features from your app, please see the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ept id=\"p1\">How to use the .NET server SDK]</ept> topic."
    },
    {
      "content": "If your app makes use of the authentication features, you will also need to register an OWIN middleware.",
